Dear Sirs:

Happy Dussehara to all!!!

It is indeed a matter of shame. However, before making any comments it would
be pertinent to confirm that the accused is a PIO. If that be the case and
no action has been taken on the FIR a formal notice must be sent to the SP
or otherwise a complaint case may be filed with the concerned magistrate.

Could we have more factual information on the whole episode.

Best regards,

Sreejit Mohanty

